          <presentation>
            <material>
              <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;p&gt;What&amp;#x27;s wrong? `const deck = new Deck(); deck.cards.push(new Card(&amp;#x27;Hearts&amp;#x27;));`&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
            </material>
